text: Momba may refer to: * Momba, Zambia, a former kingdom in Zambia * Momba District, a district in Tanzania * Momba Station, a pastoral lease in outback New South Wales, Australia *Momba River, a river in Tanzania and Zambia *Momba, Gourma, settlement in Fada N'gourma Department, Gourma Province, Burkina Faso *Momba, name of the Wicked Witch of the West in The Wonderful Wizard of Oz (1910 film)
title: Momba
